@host = https://localhost:7199
@hostHttp = http://localhost:5299

### Reference — health check (works out of the box)
GET {{hostHttp}}/resilience/health

### Pre-built — reset upstream failure counter between resilience tests
POST {{hostHttp}}/upstream/reset

### Exercise 1 — list all quotes
GET {{hostHttp}}/quotes

### Exercise 2 — get by id
GET {{hostHttp}}/quotes/1
###
GET {{hostHttp}}/quotes/999

### Exercise 2 — create a quote
POST {{hostHttp}}/quotes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Stay hungry, stay foolish.",
  "author": "Steve Jobs"
}

### Exercise 3 — enriched quote (upstream may fail without resilience policies)
GET {{hostHttp}}/quotes/1/enriched

### Exercise 6 — throttling (send rapidly to trigger 429 after 5 requests in 10s)
GET {{hostHttp}}/quotes/1/enriched
